set_map
DW_wibble creator help
set_map

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_map -  Function to set the map to one of the standard areas.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_map(string area)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^area%^RESET%^ - the area of Discworld the map should cover.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Function to set the map to one of the standard areas.  If you wish to
have the map cover a custom area use setup_map.

.EP

